sections.heading: Sections; applicability; how construed
sections.text: Sections 73-301 to 73-306 shall not apply to the Nebraska Consultants' Competitive Negotiation Act, the State Building Construction Alternatives Act, the State Park System Construction Alternatives Act, sections 39-2808 to 39-2823, or section 57-1503.Sections 7
